法規內容.條文內容:
The Inspection fees mentioned under these regulations are as follows :
1. Inspection fees;
2. Examination fees;
3. Assessment fees;
4. Registration fees;
5. Certificate fees;
6. On-site fees;
7. Testing fees; and
8. Service fees.
Fees shall be counted & collected in New Taiwan Dollars. The amount of mantissa less than one NT dollar will not be counted.
